node.text: We say “we should” and “we shouldn’t” way too much in my opinion. But thanks to @halotopcreamery, snack time decisions can be that much easier. Halo Top Dairy Pints are a good source of protein with less than 380 calories. And there are keto options, too. So grab a pint and join me – you’ll be glad you did. #ad #StopShouldingYourself
